message: International Justice Mission UMNis a group of students who are passionate about ending slavery for good. TONIGHT we get to respond. It's our biggest event of the semester and I'd love for you to come join us if you've always wanted to be a part of IJM or never heard of it! We'd love to see you there. There will be worship, prayer, food, and a time for response. Our God CARES deeply about the injustices in the world and tonight we get to stand and say the same.
